title: OpenSUSE Slowroll Asks Community For A New Name
description:
Recently OpenSUSE Slowroll showed up with a release cycle slower than Tumbleweed but faster than Leap however now they're asking the community for a new name and as you might expect, some of the names are kind of terrible
